24 Aug 2018 14:56






Magic and the development of magic could, in its own right, be an anomaly unto itself. I am neither equipped, nor willing to broach magic under any single anomaly (we have several systems that try and I don't want to tread on that ground). I don't think making the development of magic an article would, in and of itself, be an altogether interesting concept, as this article exists within a headcanon space for me, as an author, where anyone can develop the ability to use magic through various means and ways, some of which are easily accessible, and some of which are very much not. That's not really a story I wanted to tell, nor do I think it would have been conducive to the pacing of the article as it is.







